          Both Swica and Sanitas offer the standard suite of basic insurance models, allowing expats to choose based on their preferences for cost and access to care. Premium-wise, both are in the moderate to upper-moderate range, reflecting their quality of service and comprehensive offerings. Swica is often perceived as slightly more premium in its pricing but justifies this with exceptional service.
