            <strong>Swica (mySwica app & portal):</strong> Swica's digital platform is consistently praised for its intuitive design, ease of use, and comprehensive features. Expats can easily submit claims by photo, view policy documents, manage personal details, find doctors, and access telemedicine services. The English version is well-maintained.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Sanitas (Sanitas Portal app & online portal):</strong> Sanitas also boasts an excellent digital offering. The Sanitas Portal app is highly rated for its functionality, allowing users to manage all aspects of their insurance, submit invoices, access digital health coaching, and utilize services like medication ordering or symptom checkers. Their English digital services are also very comprehensive.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p>While both are top-tier, some users might find the mySwica interface slightly more streamlined, whereas the Sanitas Portal might offer a broader range of integrated digital health services.</p>

        <h3>Expat-Friendliness: Language, Support, and Onboarding</h3>
