          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Onboarding for New Arrivals:</strong> Both insurers have experience catering to expatriates and provide resources and information to help new arrivals understand the Swiss health system and get their insurance set up. Swica's proactive customer service is often highlighted by expats as particularly helpful during the initial phase.
          </li>
        </ul>

