            <strong>Alternative Medicine & Wellness:</strong> Sanitas is well-regarded for its extensive supplementary coverage for alternative medicine. Swica also provides good options, especially with its Completa Top and Optima plans, the latter also offering significant contributions (up to CHF 800/year) to gym memberships and wellness activities. Sanitas encourages wellness through its Active App and various plan contributions.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Handling of Pre-existing Conditions</h3>
        <p>
